name: AI Generated Nude Portrait #7
description: In 2018 SuperRare and Christie's partnered with Jason Bailey and enlisted Robbie Barrat to create “AI Generated Nude Portrait #7”, which he intended as 300 separate frames of a single artwork.  A small handful of these original NFTs are known to still exist. We’ll call them “Robbies”. On April 5th, 2021, frame 269 sold for 125ETH ($265K). Generative sales by @dblockdotorg.
